77,316,'position','Creative and Marketing Director'),(1078,316,'_position','field_5f2480260a26a'),(1079,316,'instagram_link',''),(1080,316,'_instagram_link','field_5f223c2958cfe'),(1081,318,'_edit_lock','1598307605:2'),(1082,318,'_edit_last','2'),(1083,318,'info_section_0_header','Ideas We Highlight:'),(1084,318,'_info_section_0_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1085,318,'info_section_0_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li>We need to commit to Jesus’ lifestyle if we want his life, which requires both theology and practice (know it, but also do it)</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognize the value of Jesus’ offer of a gospel-centered life</li>\r\n 	<li>We practice this together as we learn about Jesus’ lifestyle through the teaching of scripture on Sundays, relational “mirrors” in Community Groups, and pragmatic discussions of ethics in Icon Groups</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1086,318,'_info_section_0_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1087,318,'info_section_1_header','Reference:'),(1088,318,'_info_section_1_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1089,318,'info_section_1_content','<p class=\"\"><em>The Ruthless Elimination of Hurry: How to Stay Emotionally Healthy and Spiritually Alive in the Chaos of the Modern World </em>by John Mark Comer. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Ruthless-Elimination-Hurry-Emotionally-Spiritually/dp/0525653090/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=\">Amazon</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">Matthew 11:28-30, ESV</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">“Come to me, all who labor and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest. Take my yoke upon you, and learn from me, for I am gentle and lowly in heart, and you will find rest for your souls. For my yoke is easy, and my burden is light.”</p>'),(1090,318,'_info_section_1_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1091,318,'info_section_2_header','Reflection:'),(1092,318,'_info_section_2_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1093,318,'info_section_2_content','<ol>\r\n 	<li>If you’re a leader at Icon, take a look at the outcomes in your life. The results you are getting reveal how you are defining “the good life.” How are you living and defining that on a day-to-day basis? Are the outcomes you’re seeing in line with the way of Jesus?</li>\r\n 	<li>If you’re not part of Icon, where do people in your church learn to follow Jesus? Is there a place where and/or a process by which people learn and practice together?</li>\r\n</ol>'),(1094,318,'_info_section_2_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1095,318,'info_section','3'),(1096,318,'_info_section','field_5f2b4a3d9fe68'),(1097,318,'video','<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rvL7Ahjs9bU\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1098,318,'_video','field_5f29d6a25f5d0'),(1099,318,'audio','<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"180\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\" seamless src=\"https://share.transistor.fm/e/50e9e96c\"></iframe>'),(1100,318,'_audio','field_5f2b2b50f19b4'),(1101,318,'apple_podcast_link','https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/following-jesus-discipleship-ep-2/id1501462752?i=1000468124054'),(1102,318,'_apple_podcast_link','field_5f29d6ab5f5d1'),(1103,318,'spotify_link','https://open.spotify.com/episode/0nMlCdAf5yRHHw5aG4ywAm'),(1104,318,'_spotify_link','field_5f29d6b35f5d2'),(1105,318,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_podcast_series','9'),(1106,318,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(1107,71,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_podcast_series','8'),(1108,320,'_thumbnail_id','72'),(1109,320,'video','<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/y9i8uK6uaIg\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1110,320,'_video','field_5f29d6a25f5d0'),(1111,320,'audio','<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"180\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\" seamless src=\"https://share.transistor.fm/e/fc044e98\"></iframe>'),(1112,320,'_audio','field_5f2b2b50f19b4'),(1113,320,'apple_podcast_link','https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/peace-needs-a-focus-relational-practices-ep-2/id1501462752?i=1000470852468'),(1114,320,'_apple_podcast_link','field_5f29d6ab5f5d1'),(1115,320,'spotify_link','https://open.spotify.com/episode/3pP9RdN4iOJhvmJ8kMIbax'),(1116,320,'_spotify_link','field_5f29d6b35f5d2'),(1117,320,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(1118,320,'info_section_0_header','Ideas We Highlight'),(1119,320,'_info_section_0_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1120,320,'info_section_0_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li>Why “self-help” will never be enough because the point shouldn’t be the “self”</li>\r\n 	<li>Misguided evaluations of the “effectiveness” of spiritual disciplines</li>\r\n 	<li>How we close the gap between who we are and who we want to be</li>\r\n 	<li>Why a culture of “live your dream, speak your truth” is opposed to the Gospel</li>\r\n 	<li>Practical ways to love God and others when we’re working from home, parenting without an escape, and trying to check in on people in our community</li>\r\n 	<li>Co-opting mantras for the sake of spiritual formation</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1121,320,'_info_section_0_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1122,320,'info_section_1_header','Reference'),(1123,320,'_info_section_1_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1124,320,'info_section_1_content','<p class=\"\"><em>Practices of Love: Spiritual Disciplines for the Life of the World</em> by Kyle David Bennett. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N10VZKQ/ref=cm_sw_em_r_mt_dp_U_SbkJEb4G998Z0\">Amazon</a>.</p>'),(1125,320,'_info_section_1_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1126,320,'info_section_2_header','Reflection'),(1127,320,'_info_section_2_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1128,320,'info_section_2_content','Find a short meditation or “breath prayer” to practice this week that will remind you of the truth that it’s not all about you, and reorient you to your gospel purpose. Here are some of the ideas from the episode:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>“I’m made for God and neighbor, not myself”</li>\r\n 	<li>\"Lord Jesus Christ, Son of God, have mercy on me, a sinner.\"</li>\r\n 	<li>“Christ is all and we are his”</li>\r\n 	<li>“It’s not about me”</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1129,320,'_info_section_2_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1130,320,'info_section','3'),(1131,320,'_info_section','field_5f2b4a3d9fe68'),(1132,320,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_podcast_series','8'),(1133,320,'_dp_original','71'),(1134,320,'_edit_lock','1598404773:1'),(1135,320,'_edit_last','1'),(1136,318,'_thumbnail_id','70'),(1137,279,'_thumbnail_id','268'),(1138,322,'info_section_0_header','Ideas We Highlight:'),(1139,322,'_info_section_0_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1140,322,'info_section_0_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diagnostic questions to assess your physical, mental/emotional, and spiritual health</li>\r\n 	<li>Strategies for responding to unhealth in different areas of your life</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1141,322,'_info_section_0_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1142,322,'info_section_1_header','Reference:'),(1143,322,'_info_section_1_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1144,322,'info_section_1_content','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://michaelhyatt.com/ideal-week/\">Creating an Ideal Week</a> with Michael Hyatt</li>\r\n 	<li>Using a <a href=\"https://www.simplemost.com/feeling-wheel-will-help-better-describe-emotions/#:~:text=The%20wheel%20has%20six%20core,Adult%20Children%20of%20Alcoholics\">feelings wheel</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.iconchurch.org/leadershippodcast\">Season 2</a> on Relational Practices and building a rule of life</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Screwtape-Letters-C-S-Lewis/dp/0060652934\"><em>The Screwtape Letters</em></a> by C.S. Lewis</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1145,322,'_info_section_1_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1146,322,'info_section_2_header','Reflection:'),(1147,322,'_info_section_2_header','field_5f2b4a4b9fe69'),(1148,322,'info_section_2_content','Assess your health and respond to unhealth\r\n\r\nSet aside time to reflect on the diagnostic questions for each category. Block out thirty minutes on the schedule, or take 10 minutes and review one area at a time over the course of a day or a few days. Actually write down your responses and be specific!\r\n\r\n<strong>Assess Physical Health:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>How’s your energy level? Do you have energy to do the things you love?</li>\r\n 	<li>How are you sleeping? Enough? Regularly?</li>\r\n 	<li>How’s your physical health? Exercise, eating, significant weight gain or loss?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Assess Mental/Emotional Health:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Are you experiencing fear or anxiety? How would you rate your level of stress?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do your emotional responses match the stimulus? (i.e. outsized emotional reactions)</li>\r\n 	<li>Who are you spending time with? Are your relationships healthy and are they people who are fueling you?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Assess Spiritual Health:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>What spiritual disciplines are you regularly practicing?</li>\r\n 	<li>How is not gathering with your church community affecting you?</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1149,322,'_info_section_2_content','field_5f2b4a4f9fe6a'),(1150,322,'info_section','3'),(1151,322,'_info_section','field_5f2b4a3d9fe68'),(1152,322,'video','<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QcksSKVWx8I\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),(1153,322,'_video','field_5f29d6a25f5d0'),(1154,322,'audio','<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"180\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\" seamless src=\"https://share.transistor.fm/e/3c7b899b\"></iframe>'),(1155,322,'_audio','field_5f2b2b50f19b4'),(1156,322,'apple_podcast_link','https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/am-i-healthy-a-strategy-for-re-entry-ep-1/id1501462752?i=1000485716621'),(1157,322,'_apple_podcast_link','field_5f29d6ab5f5d1'),(1158,322,'spotify_link','https://open.spotify.com/episode/4pTargiyy9Yp5DpTvgDkme'),(1159,322,'_spotify_link',