ticle/make-habits-not-resolutions/%C2%A0\">here</a> or visit <a href=\"https://www.thecommonrule.org/\">The Common Rule website</a> for additional resources</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><em>Practices of Love: Spiritual Disciplines for the Life of the World</em> by Kyle David Bennett. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Practices-Love-Spiritual-Disciplines-World/dp/1587434032/ref=sr_1_1?crid=2GW9SXIRJLZHP&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=practices%20of%20love%20spiritual%20disciplines%20for%20the%20life%20of%20the%20world&amp;qid=1585241864&amp;sprefix=practices%20of%20love%2Caps%2C220&amp;sr=8-1\">Amazon</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><em>Crafting a Rule of Life: An Invitation to the Well-Ordered Way</em> by Stephen Macchia. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Crafting-Rule-Life-Invitation-Well-Ordered/dp/0830835644/ref=tmm_pap_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=1585242011&amp;sr=8-1\">Amazon</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><em>The Eternal Current: How a Practice-Based Faith Can Save Us from Drowning</em> by Aaron Niequist. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Eternal-Current-Practice-Based-Faith-Drowning/dp/0735291160/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=1585241950&amp;sr=8-1\">Amazon</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><em>The Ruthless Elimination of Hurry: How to Stay Emotionally Healthy and Spiritually Alive in the Chaos of the Modern World</em> by John Mark Comer. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Ruthless-Elimination-Hurry-Emotionally-Spiritually/dp/0525653090/ref=sr_1_2?dchild=1&amp;keywords=the%20ruthless%20elimination%20of%20hurry%20john%20mark%20comer&amp;qid=1585243676&amp;sr=8-2&amp;swrs=0CCF9C088B0413F24D916E8085DF40C7\">Amazon</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><em>The Renovation of the Heart: Putting on the Character of Christ</em> by Dallas Willard. Find it on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Renovation-Heart-Putting-Character-Christ/dp/1615216324/ref=tmm_pap_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=1585241749&amp;sr=8-1\">Amazon</a>.</p>'),(26,7,'_resource_row_0_con